ic reconnection forms concave-up\nmagnetic field that lifts plasma into the filament. During this time, the free\nmagnetic energy in the models increases by 0.2$\\times$10$^{31}$ ergs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Nov 2019 16:27:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
