e expense of communication\nbandwidth and computation, a tradeoff that may be advantageous on modern\nmassively parallel supercomputers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Nov 2019 18:07:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-18"}
